import { createContext } from 'react'

interface Btc2xFliTokenMarketDataValues {
  prices?: number[][]

  marketcaps?: number[][]
  volumes?: number[][]

  latestMarketCap?: number
  latestVolume?: number

const Btc2xFliMarketData = createContext<Btc2xFliTokenMarketDataValues>({})

export default Btc2xFliMarketData
